

== Installation

Ensure boost development libraries are installed.  E.g. on Debian...

aptitude install libboost-program-options-dev
aptitude install libboost-filesystem-dev

And the C++ toolchain:

aptitude install build-essential

Then compile the code:

g++ main.cpp rtf.cpp ccontrolword.cpp aux.cpp -lboost_filesystem -lboost_program_options -o rtf-filter

Then ensure that resulting program is executable:

chmod +x rtf-filter

